original_title: Woof! Woof!! Uncle Matty's Ultimate Guide to Dog Training
overview: Woof Woof: Uncle Matty's Guide to Dog Training offers a friendly and funny approach to raising a dog. Host Matthew Margolies speaks with humor, warmth, and authority when talking both to his pupil dogs and to his audience.
title: Woof! Woof!! Uncle Matty's Ultimate Guide to Dog Training
